kubeadm join k8smaster.example.net:6443 --token ppenf7.xi9p1kr9n93sx3p7 \
	--discovery-token-ca-cert-hash sha256:2044ead7a4f3a1436be75c2fb855ec9ec3aa8e4a3a57396d1f23dd04e677fae6 \
	--control-plane 

Then you can join any number of worker nodes by running the following on each as root:

kubeadm join k8smaster.example.net:6443 --token ppenf7.xi9p1kr9n93sx3p7 \
	--discovery-token-ca-cert-hash sha256:2044ead7a4f3a1436be75c2fb855ec9ec3aa8e4a3a57396d1f23dd04e677fae6
